    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "準決勝、注目の勝者は『STROBOLIGHTS』！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the semifinals‚ the winner we've all been waiting for is… STROBOLIGHTS!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3866.6666667000004,
          "startTime": 4.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_popper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4066.6666667,
          "startTime": 4.8666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_popper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3866.6666667000004,
          "startTime": 4.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ⅢX、BIG4には力及ばずここで敗退となりました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX‚ unable to overcome BIG4‚ are eliminated here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4666666667,
      "endTime": 11.3548753262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "……嘘でしょ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're kidding…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5333333333,
      "endTime": 13.879115661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "（相手がBIG4だったから？　息が合ってなかった？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Was it because our opponent was BIG4? Was our teamwork off?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0666666667,
      "endTime": 18.8619273822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "（……いえ、理由なんてどうでもいいわ）\n（私はこんなとこで足踏みなんかしていられないのに！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…No‚ the reason doesn't matter.)\n(I can't be stuck here!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0666666667,
      "endTime": 26.5843762079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "（ドイツ人の母親に似て、生まれた時から金髪碧眼）\n（この髪と目の色が、子供の頃は嫌で仕方なかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I've had blonde hair and blue eyes since I was born‚ taking after my German mother.)\n(I hated this hair and eye color so much when I was a kid.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "endTime": 40.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "（この変な見た目のせいで）\n（誰も、一緒に遊んでくれないんだと思ってたから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Because of this weird appearance‚)\n(I thought no one wanted to play with me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9666666667,
      "endTime": 46.5807707469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "（……きっかけはなんだったかしら）\n（確か、可愛いワンピースを親に買ってもらって）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㄴ\n(I think my parents bought me a cute dress‚)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2,
      "endTime": 57.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、学校の人に見られるのが怖くて……）\n（かわりに、知り合いが誰もいない街に出掛けたのよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(but I was scared to let anyone at school see me in it…)\n(So I went to a town where I didn't know anyone.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2666666667,
      "endTime": 66.1103859584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "（そうしたらびっくり、事務所にスカウトされたわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(And then‚ to my surprise‚ I was scouted by an agency!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4,
      "endTime": 72.91111106870001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "（私みたいな子でも可愛くしてくれる）\n（ファッションって凄いんだって、そう思ったのよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Fashion is amazing‚ it can even make someone like me look cute.)\n(That's what I thought.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2,
      "endTime": 80.61594104740001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "（ファッション業界に少しでも近づきたくて）\n（モデルの仕事を始めて、そこから先はとんとん拍子）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I wanted to be even a little closer to the fashion world‚)\n(so I started working as a model‚ and things just took off from there.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333333333,
      "endTime": 90.53333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "（あんなに嫌だった金髪もここでは大きな武器だった）\n（あのパリコレの舞台にだって立ったんだから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(My blonde hair‚ which I hated so much‚ was a big asset here.)\n(I even stood on the stage of Paris Fashion Week.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7666666667,
      "endTime": 98.7866211573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "（ファッションの仕事をする夢だって、一時は叶った）\n（……でも）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(My dream of working in fashion… I achieved it for a while.)\n(…But.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3,
      "endTime": 106.1999999047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡り、VENUSグランプリ準々決勝後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rewinding time‚ to after the Venus Grand Prix quarterfinals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6666666667,
      "endTime": 110.1333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、今日も勝ちました～っと\nえーと、これでkanaってベスト4なんだっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ we won again today~.\nSo… that means Kana's in the top four‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1333333333,
      "endTime": 119.1592143694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ\n私達以外は、順当にBIG4が勝ち上がっているわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nThe other three are BIG4‚ as expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3333333333,
      "endTime": 125.2278596339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "んーと、ベスト4はkanaとBIG4が三組……\nあれ？　BIG『4』なのに一組足らなくない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ the top four are Kana and three BIG4 teams…\nHuh? There should be four BIG4 teams‚ but there's one missing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4333333333,
      "endTime": 137.7933617486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "今回グランプリに出場しているのは三組だけ\n最後の一組、いえ一人は……出ていないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Only three BIG4 groups are competing in the Grand Prix this time.\nThe last group‚ or rather‚ person… isn't participating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138,
      "endTime": 147.36666666669998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "何それ、意味分かんない\nま、kanaにはどうでもいいことだけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? That doesn't make sense.\nWhatever‚ it doesn't matter to Kana~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5,
      "endTime": 154.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "私達の次の対戦相手は『STROBOLIGHTS』\n半年前にBIG4入り、それからランクを維持してるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our next opponent is STROBOLIGHTS.\nThey entered BIG4 six months ago and have maintained their rank since then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4,
      "endTime": 162.6567125593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "キャリアも実績も十分の、実力派グループね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're a skilled group with plenty of experience and achievements.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.8666666667,
      "endTime": 167.01730148000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_02_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "詳しいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know a lot about them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.2333333333,
      "endTime": 168.61242631270002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
